So, the Trump Presidential Library. Ideas, anyone? Here are a few of mine:

- Pay a fee to use a golden toilet;
- Full-scale mock-up of the Capitol to ransack;
- Sign your name on a mock-up of the wall;
- Beautiful chocolate cake in the cafeteria.¬†
- A life-sized cut-out of a North Korean general to salute.¬†

Other ideas?
